    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Artifacts, usually flexible, often textiles, used to cover or conceal interior spaces, surfaces, or furnishings, especially for protection, warmth, or embellishment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
